As a user(customer) 
I want to leave a rewiev
So that I can express my opinian

Scope

The card functionality
The posibility add the comment in the item's card
It should work in Chorome, Mozilla, Safari brousers
It should also works in Mobile


Pre condition:

The Customer is registered in online shop


Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1:User can sucesfully leave a rewiev in the item card
Given: User is in the item card page
When: Click on the "Leave Rewiev" button 
And: Select the numbers of the "Stars" which expres the impressing fmom the item
And:Fill the "Review title" field
And:Fill the "Review " field
And: Click on the "Publish" button 
Then: The comment is added


Scenario 2:User can sucesfully leave a rewiev in the item card without fillig required fields
Given: User is in the item card page
When: Click on the "Leave Rewiev" button 
And: Don't select the numbers of the "Stars" which expres the impressing from the item
And:Fill the "Review title" field
And: Click on the "Publish" button 
Then: The warning message is shown, the comment is not added


Scenario3 :User can sucesfully leave a rewiev in the item card without fillig required fields
Given: User is in the item card page
When: Click on the "Leave Rewiev" button 
And: Select the numbers of the "Stars" which expres the impressing from the item
And:Leave the "Review title" or "Rewiev" field empty
And: Click on the "Publish" button 
Then: The warning message is shown, the comment is not added








